
This is the CDN configuration for the next.ft.com presentation tier.

It features :-

- Deploy (or rollback) in under 6 seconds using the Fastly API.
- A developer-oriented workflow - deploy to staging, execute a test suite and deploy to production.
- Balances the load across multiple regions (based on origin of traffic and backend health).
- System state can be emulated with request headers.
- Multi-region routing + ability to override

